Gosub INIT_CTYBRNSEE From WMC1EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_DEPBRN From WMC1EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_CRYBRN From WMC1EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_CRYNAMBRN From WMC1EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_NTT From WMC1EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_NTTNAM From WMC1EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_SITFAM From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
