Gosub INIT_ADT From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_CHD From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_FCY From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_PRF From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_SRV From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_CPY From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_NBRCTR From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_NBRCHD From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
Gosub INIT_NBRRIB From WMC2EMPLOID : Gosub TESTALLSTAT
